. Upload Your Resume: Start by uploading your resume in PDF format. 2. Enter Your Query: Use the chat interface to ask questions or request specific tasks (e.g., "Find jobs in data science"). 3. Interact with the Assistant: The assistant will guide you through job searches, resume analysis, and cover letter generation. 4. Download Results: Save the generated cover letters or other documents as needed.   python and flask stack  
